channel.title: Project Astrocma - 317 - Models, Bosses, and much more! Looking for Help
channel.description:
Hey Guys, its me, Mike!
So, about 3 weeks ago, I was thinking of which base I should use to make a server, and guess who I stumbled upon, talking to? Aintaro! He said he'd give me his base, so he gave me the links and whatnot, and guess what? I've been coding his base for the last 3 weeks, and this is what ive got! :).
Updates since Aintaro last worked from it:
Interfaces! Learned some photoshop and did a shitload of them. Bosses. Not just the main ones, the lower level ones too. Pk points made to a perfection. Pk arenas. Duel arena in progress (finish it yourself or wait for next release.) Castle wars in progress (same shit as above.) Customs added to the ones he already had. New home. New shops. New models, stances, and other crap. Things you won't notice, but make a great deal. Client is very high-tech right now (I dont have any other words to describe it, so why not high-tech? .) 'Page Down' Shortcut for a snapshot of the game. Alot of other crap I can't remember atm.
Here are some pics that will let you decide if you want to help or not ;).

Like I said, if you want to help, either PM me here, add my MSN (stolarzm@hotmail.com), or simply leave a comment. If your gonna leave a comment or PM me, here's the format i'd like to see:
First name: Expierience: Time your are on a day: Rep: What you can do: Your time zone: Proof of work (optional, will help though): Website (optional, will help though):
Thanks agian. Mike.
